   History
   ¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
      1.0  - First release.

      1.01 - When you quitted the game, the Workbench background colour on
             AGA machines could be altered.

      1.02 - Slightly changed the in-game information.

      1.03 - Added a title music.

      1.04 - If a mouse or screen blanker was running and you started
             Croins from a screen with a resolution different than PAL, the
             game screen could result severely distorted.
           - Changed the speed of the title music (now it is the original
             one).

      1.05 - Now you can control the ship by using the keyboard.
           - Now you can disable the joystick-down switch to avoid
             accidental activation of the hyperspace (use the space-bar
             instead).
           - Some other minor changes.


